Cavaliere di Gran Croce (the highest distinction in Italy), Cavaliere del Lavoro, Commandeur de L'Ordre des Arts et des Lettres, awarded the Legion of Honour, combines Garavani with as many honours as each of its customers' husbands.
"I have always noticed his refinement, his calm, his well-groomed and perfect appearance," admits D'Arenberg.
The last time I saw him was a month ago at a gala dinner at the Museum de Orsay.
